WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:26.660
So yeah, saying you believe in CD19 positive stem cells and multiple myeloma is kind of like saying you believe in aliens. But I think we're making some believers out of people. So the concept is that potentially there's this B cell like CD19 positive multiple myeloma cell that's acting as kind of a reservoir for a small amount for the bulk of myeloma to come back after patients relapse.

00:00:26.660 --> 00:00:42.060
And there have been some studies that suggest this, other studies that refute this, but some looking at low-level microscopy in patients that are CD19 negative by flow that actually show a very small expression of CD19 on their multiple myeloma cells.

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:47.160
So maybe there's something there for dual targeting that could potentially mitigate antigen escape.

00:00:48.740 --> 00:00:56.480
And the rationale for designing this BCMA-CD19 dual targeting CAR-T was partially.

00:00:56.620 --> 00:01:04.260
But partially also to make a versatile CAR and then also would limit the development of anti-CAR antibodies in the future.

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:10.340
So this is a dual targeting CAR-T cell with a loop configuration of both binding sites.

00:01:10.340 --> 00:01:18.060
It's lentiviral vector transduction, 401BB co-stimulatory domain, and the next, actually next day manufacturing of the CAR.

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:26.580
The majority of the time it takes is the quality checks that take to get to this vein-to-vein time of about...

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:28.100
12 to 14 days.

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:36.760
So the CAR-T is actually manufactured 22 to 36 hours over, basically overnight in ex vivo culture medium with IL-2 stimulation.

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:40.600
And then the, there's no ex vivo expansion step.

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:45.040
All of the expansion of the CAR-T takes place in vivo in patients.

00:01:46.220 --> 00:01:55.720
And this actually has led to, regardless of which dose level was tested, the same peak expansion among patients in the phase one trials.

00:01:55.720 --> 00:01:56.540
And the conservative.

00:01:56.540 --> 00:01:59.080
The conservative estimate is a vein-to-vein time of 14 to 16 days.

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:02.340
I would say we've seen more about 11 to 12 days.

